{"title":"hexo+github搭建线上blog(主题)","date":"2016-10-26T07:31:16.000Z","slug":"hexo-3","tags":["hexo","tool"],"updated":"2018-10-25T08:20:03.294Z","content":"<h2 id=\"如何修改主题？\"><a href=\"#如何修改主题？\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"如何修改主题？\"></a>如何修改主题？</h2><ol>\n<li><p>进入<a href=\"https://hexo.io/themes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">主题列表页面</a>, 可以看到一系列主题。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>点击缩略图进入demo，点击主题名进入对应的github\b仓库。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>挑选喜欢的主题，下载git项目，放置到 <code>/themes</code> 路径下。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git clone xxx themes/name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>进入<code>_config.yml</code>文件，修改<code>theme</code>的值为主题项目名即可。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"以下是两款我喜欢的主题\"><a href=\"#以下是两款我喜欢的主题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"以下是两款我喜欢的主题\"></a>以下是两款我喜欢的主题</h2><h2 id=\"next\"><a href=\"#next\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"next\"></a>next</h2><p><a href=\"http://theme-next.iissnan.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">home page</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"icarus\"><a href=\"#icarus\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"icarus\"></a>icarus</h2><p><a href=\"https://blog.zhangruipeng.me/hexo-theme-icarus/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Demo</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/ppoffice/hexo-theme-icarus\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Github</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"tranquilpeak\"><a href=\"#tranquilpeak\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"tranquilpeak\"></a>tranquilpeak</h2><p><a href=\"http://louisbarranqueiro.github.io/hexo-theme-tranquilpeak/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Demo</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/LouisBarranqueiro/hexo-theme-tranquilpeak\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Github</a></p>\n","prev":{"title":"hexo+github搭建线上blog(有用的配置)","slug":"hexo-2"},"next":{"title":"hexo+github搭建线上blog(基本部分)","slug":"hexo-1"},"link":"http://qixman.github.io/post/hexo-3/","toc":[{"title":"如何修改主题？","id":"如何修改主题？","index":